	<h3>SQL's Advantatges</h3>
	<ul>
	  <li>No coding needed</li>
	  <li>Well defined standards</li>
	  <li>Portability</li>
	  <li>Interactive language</li>
	  <li>Multiple data views</li>
	</ul>
	<h3>SQL's Disadvantatges</h3>
	<ul>
	  <li>Difficult Interface</li>
	  <li>Partial Control</li>
	  <li>Implementation</li>
	  <li>Cost</li>
	</ul>
